                        from the library of the <placeName ref="https://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q1218">Jerusalem</placeName> patriarchate through
                        <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10784Michael">Michael</persName> the Metropolitan of <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC5090Petra">Petra</placeName>
                           </desc>
